name: 3 Vellum Votive Candle Holders - Damask (FREE Candle)
description:
This listing is for 3 votive candle holders with vellum damask prints.  The votive holders are 2 1/2inches tall.  3 FREE candles will be included with your order.  Once your order has been placed, add a comment with your PAYPAL payment indicating which designs you would like (1a, 1b, 2a, 2b, 3a-orange, 3b-chocolate brown).  You may mix and match or pick the same design for all three votive holders.

*For item #, click on the picture #3 for larger image*

name: 24 Vellum Votive Candle Holder WRAPS
description:
Are you a DIY type of person?  Then check out the DIY Votive Wraps.  Each set creates 24 Damask print votive wraps and comes ready for you to trim.  Note: votive holders and candles are not included.  Wraps fit votive holders 2 1/2inches tall or smaller (you'll have to trim them a little to fit anything smaller than 2 1/2inches tall).    Make sure to include the print you are interested in at checkout. 

*Each set is for one design.  Additional prints may be ordered by ordering additional sets.

<b>~Item qualifies for Free Shipping~<b>

name: Vellum Luminary - Wild Damask 8"
description:
Luminaries make not only great gifts, but they also make great home decor and affordable wedding centerpieces.  This gorgeous luminary is 8 inches tall and 3 1/2 inches in diameter.  It illuminates best with a pillar candle in the center.  

The small votive holders shown in the picture is not included and candles are not provided.
